    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Mesh convergence, pressure-flow validation, and hemolysis index comparison collectively demonstrate that the CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion met at all five operating points. Package accepted for regulatory submission support.",
